# Patient Management System (VB.NET)

A professional desktop Patient Management System developed using **VB.NET (.NET Framework 4.7)** and **Microsoft Access**.

## Features

- Modern RTL Windows Forms interface
- Patient CRUD operations
- Advanced search and filtering
- Patient image management using file paths
- Automatic Activity Log (User, Date, Time, Action Details)
- Professional printing and reporting
- Export to Excel and PDF
- Microsoft Access Database
- Clean and organized source code
- No third-party libraries

## Technologies

- VB.NET
- .NET Framework 4.7
- Windows Forms
- Microsoft Access (.accdb)
- ADO.NET (OleDb)

## Purpose

This project is intended as an educational and practical reference for developers building professional desktop applications. The source code can be reused and extended for larger management systems.

